Class VerifyGmailFunctionalityAssignment

  • java.lang.Object
    • utility.TestSetUp
      • testCases.VerifyGmailFunctionalityAssignment

  • public class VerifyGmailFunctionalityAssignment
extends TestSetUp
    Author:
    Rahul This is an assignment given from Cloud Cover to the author. This is solely belongs to Rahul and Cloud Cover. This class will open gmail.com and verify default Tab post successful login. If default tab is not primary tab, it will click on Primary tab. After that it will click on Social Tab and count number of E-mails in social tab. It will then get the sender name and subject of 12th email in Social tab. After that this class will count the total number of e-mails in social tab.
